		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
			<p rend="indent(7)">
				<placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
				<date>Novr 13th 1835</date>
			</p>
			<p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As usual had nothing new to write I<lb/> did not answer your letters
				nor have I<lb/> at present any thing interesting to say,<lb/> but not having wrote
				to you for a long<lb/> time I think you will <sic>lick</sic> to hear from<lb/> me,
				well you friend <persName>Mr Solis</persName> will have<lb/> told you we were all
				well and that we<lb/> have done all in our power to make his<lb/> stay with us as
				agreeable to him as<lb/> ;<sic>ossible</sic> we all were pleased with him,<lb/> in
					<sic>regaurd</sic> the wedding I say you acted<lb/> as if I should have done my
				self, nor<lb/> would I care if the <persName>Ettings</persName> and the whole<lb/>
				<add>משפחה</add> were dissatisfied<lb/>
				<add>רבי מארדכי</add> ought not to have<lb/> performed, he should have known that
				to<lb/> take from you the performing was done<lb/> out of spite and on no other
				acct. you<lb/> acted very right not to take any fee from<lb/>
				<persName>Marx</persName>, I hope your Congregation will<lb/> acknowledge you acted
				right in all the proceeding, <sic>buring</sic> and wedding, your<lb/> discourses are
				very good <persName>Philip Cohen</persName><lb/> has been reading one of them is
				much<lb/> pleased with it I shall send them to<lb/> you soon, we had yesterday
				the.....<lb/> bration at Least good very gential<lb/> people attended all very
					<sic>Quite</sic> we are<lb/> all thank God very well and all send
					<sic>there</sic><lb/> love to you and remember us to all our</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p><sic>freinds</sic> tell <persName>Mrs Joseph</persName> she must let us<lb/> know
				when she knows what give our Love to<lb/> her<lb/> I remain Your friend <persName
					role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName><lb/> when <sic>appportunity</sic> offers
				send me your last <sic>discours</sic></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">The revd <addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">No 86 Walnut Street</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">
				<placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
			</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">single</p>
		</body>
